          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Kleptocracy Asset Recovery Rewards Act</strong> </p> <p>This bill establishes in the Department of the Treasury the Kleptocracy Asset Recovery Rewards Program. The program may provide rewards to individuals furnishing information leading to the restraining, seizure, forfeiture, or repatriation of stolen assets linked to foreign government corruption.</p> <p>]]></text>
